text:
Oh, sorry about that. Looks like the preparations are still
ongoing. Can you wait a bit longer until you're called?

The longer I wait,
the more nervous I get...

Did Juri ever get nervous
before a match?

A match... Well,
there were things to do back then.

During those times, did you do some light stretching
or... engage in unrelated conversations?

I see. Then...
What did you have for breakfast this morning?

Huh... Onigiri and fish sausage...
Well, I didn't have much time...!

Haha, that's fine.
At least you had a good meal.

Haha...
Yeah, that might help me relax a bit.
